  "texts": [
    "Anscombe is sensitive to this objection, which she puts like this:",
    "[O]ne might think that when the question 'Why?'",
    "is answered by giving the intention with which the person acts […] this is also a case of a mental cause.",
    "For couldn't one recast it in the form: 'Because I wanted…' or 'Out of a desire that…'?",
    "(p. 17) Her response begins from the observation that while 'recastings' of answers to the question 'Why?'"
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "is answered by giving the intention with which the person acts […] this is also a case of a mental cause."
  ]
}